Head (
Figs. 10
B-C, 11A-C, 12A):

As long as wide, almost entirely retractable into prothorax (
Figs. 10
B-C); dorsal surface with long, fine and sparse setae on anterior and lateral regions, one stemma with convex lens laterally at base of antennifer; antennifer membranous and glabrous,as long as basal antennomere (
